headline.print_headline: Childhood Obesity Panel: 40 Million Kids Under 5 Overweight
headline.main: Childhood Obesity Panel: 40 Million Kids Under 5 Overweight

docs.lead_paragraph: An independent panel on obesity commissioned by the World Health Organization is urging governments, educators, agribusiness and food marketers to do more to help fight childhood obesity.
